

=Description=

'We are a group of 10th grade students at Four Rivers Charter Public School in Greenfield, Massachusetts. We are doing a school project in our History class about activism. Our group chose to stand behind Occupy Wall Street. We invite anyone to post anything pertaining to any Occupy around the world. We are advocating for campaign finance reform, we're trying to make the wealth gap smaller, and we believe that the top 1 percent (that can obviously afford it.) should pay higher taxes than the 99 percent!"
